                            <div class="help-item">
                                <h3 class="help-question">How to prepare for a job interview?</h3>
                                <p class="help-answer">Research the company, practice common interview questions, prepare questions to ask the interviewer, and dress appropriately.</p>
                            </div>

                            <div class="help-item">
