                                <p class="help-answer">Research industry standards, know your worth, be confident but flexible, and consider the entire compensation package.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>

                    <!-- About Section (Hidden by default) -->
                    <section id="about-section" class="hidden-section">
                        <h2 class="section-title">About CareerCin</h2>
                        <div class="about-section">
                            <p class="about-content">
                                CareerCin is a leading job portal dedicated to connecting talented professionals with top employers.
                                Our mission is to make the job search process easier, faster, and more effective for both job seekers and employers.
